item.title: Yeah... HELP ME!
item.dc:creator: @mod_taharok Taharok
item.description:
@mod_taharok wrote:

If you have not been coding very long or just started, then use Testscape source and search for specific doors, ladders, portals, or levers and it will come up with somthing liek this:

if (objectID == 5960) // Mage bank lever to wildy if (absY == 4712) { if(teleblock == false) { teleportToX = 3090; teleportToY = 3956; } else if(teleblock == true) { sendMessage("A magical force stops you from teleporting."); }

And you can change the object ID to any object id you want (somthing that has action otherwise it is pointless [use moaprscaper 3.1 to do this]), and change the X and Y cords your teleing to whatever you want for teleportation. I hope this helped and Enjoy!

~Mod Taharok
